<div style="padding: 10px">
    <h1 style="text-align:center">PersianComponents</h1>
    <p class="lead">
        A set of useful UI-Components (HtmlHelper) for ASP.NET Core MVC based-on Popular JavaScript Plugins (Experimental project).
        <hr />
        <ul class="sss" style="font-size: medium;">
            <li>Easy-to-Use with just one line of code.</li>
            <li>Fully Configuralbe for each component.</li>
            <li>Add necessary CSS (to top) and JS (to down) resources automatically when you use a component and remove tags when you no longer use it.</li>
            <li>No need to deal with a specific script code for each component.</li>
            <li>Includes a Variety of components.</li>
            <li>Usable in View and PartialView.</li>
            <li>Usable with Ajax and Non-Ajax requests.</li>
            <li>Using CDN resources instead of Locale Embedded resources (Optional).</li>
            <li>Lightweight with small footprint.</li>
        </ul>
        <hr />
    </p>
</div>

